            <p><rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_II_1983">
               <rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__stephan_lang_QGW_II_II_1983">Stephan Lang, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">burger</roleName> ze
                     Wienn,</rs></rs> beurkundet, dass er <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__helena_QGW_II_II_1983">seiner <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__stephan_lang_QGW_II_I_1646">Frau</roleName> Helen, <rs type="person" ref="#pe__haunold_schuchler_QGW_II_I_1557">Haunolts des
